        <h3>What's Old is New Again</h3>
        <p>Responsive Web Design (RWD) is no longer a new idea. And yet, in an industry where trends seem to come and go overnight, the principles behind RWD are increasingly relevant. Let’s revisit these principles and look at how RWD is used to help designers and developers deliver a first class product to the user.</p>
